Blue sky bagels is a traditional small town cafe and bakery in a growing city. Whether you're a regular coming in for coffee or just passing through town, blue sky will greet you with a warm hello and an even warmer bagel. Their food is made fresh, including cookies and cream cheese. Blue sky is a local favorite! Honestly nothing better than a fresh bagel with butter and honey, or get fancy and have them make you a delicious sandwich. While the downtown store is the best and original location, there are 3 other locations that have the same positivity and great food. The blue sky staff is a family that includes their customers. Sadly no gluten free options but gluten is better in bread anyway!

Also do yourself a favor and get some kombucha! It's locally brewed and on-tap with a choice of two flavors that are frequently updated. Always delicious and also very good for you!
